'''Bia Kawaii Br''' is a highly popular world creator in VRChat, recognized for her dedicated work and the warm community she has built around her projects. She has been on the platform since '''2021''', accumulating 5 years of experience and a deep understanding of the Brazilian VRChat community.

Bia is a cisgender woman and autistic — and as she is mute, she communicates on the platform through other means, which has never been a barrier to her enormous presence and charisma in the community.

== Achievements ==

Bia is well known for being the creator of [[Community:Cruzeiro_Brasil|Cruzeiro Brasil]], one of the most celebrated worlds on the platform. She has also won the '''Space Jam''' twice — a space-themed world creation contest held by VRChat in partnership with the National Space Society, where creators are challenged to build immersive experiences inspired by space exploration.

* 🏆 '''[https://wiki.vrchat.com/wiki/Space_Jam_2025 Space Jam 2025]''' — [https://vrchat.com/home/world/wrld_407e6571-b66b-4688-a5de-8d040ce9a53a Stellarya]
* 🏆 '''[https://wiki.vrchat.com/wiki/Space_Jam_2026 Space Jam 2026]''' — [https://vrchat.com/home/world/wrld_13cabd83-9f05-44a0-87e3-716aa3fc484c StarlightLab]

== World Creation Style ==

Bia stands out for her focus on '''performance and optimization''', ensuring her worlds can be enjoyed by players with all types of hardware. Another remarkable trait is her ability to translate her maps into '''more than 20 languages''', making her creations accessible to a truly global audience.

Today, Bia also leads national projects within VRChat, and is a beloved figure among both players and the VRChat team itself.

== Birthday Tradition 🎂 ==

Every year on '''April 23rd''', Bia celebrates her birthday with the community in a very special way: all of her worlds offer '''free VIP access for 24 hours'''. It's her way of giving back to everyone who has supported her throughout the years!

== Appearance ==

You can recognize Bia Kawaii Br by her distinctive avatar: pink hair, pink cat ears, pink eyes, fair skin, and an elegant suit with a skirt — along with a shiny fluffy pink tail!

